<body style="text-align: justify">

    <div class="team-section">

        <p class="white-text">
            Welcome to Fishing Radar! The goal of this website is to provide a social media platform focused on anything fishing
            related. Users can feel free to share pictures of fish they caught, where they caught it, cool fishing supply stores, and more.
        </p>

        <h2 class="white-text">About the Development Team</h2>

        <p class="white-text">
            We are a team of 4 developers, all Master of Computer Science students at Seattle University. We all share a passion
            for fishing, and have skillsets in programming and design, and have decided to team up to build this website for anyone who shares
            the same passion for fishing. If you have any feedback or would like to get in touch with us, please see our contact information
            below and reach out. Thank you!
        </p>

        <h1 class="white-text">The Team</h1>
        <span class="border"></span>
