        </div>

        <div class="section white-text" id="p1">
            <span class="name">Francis Kogge</span>
            <span class="border"></span>
            <p>
                Hi, I'm Francis! During the spring and summer, fishing is one of my favorite outdoor activities. I love
                the serenity of the water and meeting fellow fishers. Hope you enjoy the website and share your favorite
                spots to fish and awesome catches!
            </p>
        </div>

